        "# Implementation Guidance\n",
        "\n",
        "## Chunking\n",
        "\n",
        "Use token-aware chunking with overlap. Keep chunk sizes consistent for stable retrieval.\n",
        "\n",
        "Minimum metadata per chunk:\n",
        "\n",
        "- chunk_id\n",
        "- naics_code\n",
        "- company_name\n",
        "- ticker\n",
        "- filing_year\n",
        "- item_number\n",
        "- token_count\n",
        "- source_file\n",
        "\n",
        "Including `naics_code` in every chunk allows the product to support multi-industry expansion in the future without re-indexing.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Embeddings\n",
        "\n",
        "Allowed options:\n",
        "- API: OpenAI, Gemini, Claude, Cohere\n",
        "- Local/open: Mistral, Gemma, BAAI, Qwen via Hugging Face stacks\n",
        "\n",
        "## Vector Index\n",
        "\n",
        "Preferred: FAISS\n",
        "Optional: Chroma\n",
        "\n",
        "# Retrieval Validation\n",
        "\n",
        "Run at least 5 test questions and inspect top-k chunk quality manually.\n",
        "\n",
        "# Required Outputs for Step 3\n",
        "\n",
        "- data/chunked/sec10k_chunks.parquet\n",
        "- data/embeddings/\n",
        "- data/vector_store/\n",
        "\n",
        "# Submission Checklist (Step 3)\n",
        "\n",
        "- [ ] Chunking strategy documented\n",
        "- [ ] Chunk metadata complete (including `naics_code`)\n",
        "- [ ] Embeddings generated successfully\n",
        "- [ ] Vector index built and saved\n",
        "- [ ] Top-k retrieval examples included and reviewed\n",
